item.title: Jupyter
item.description: Jupyter # pipenv install jupyterlab 参考： JupyterLab Installation Jupyter Notebook vs Jupyter Lab # Jupyter Lab is a next-generation web-based user interface for Project Jupyter Jupyter Notebook Interface is a Web-based application for authoring documents that combine live-code with narrative text, equations and visualizations. Jupyter Notebook 原名 IPython Notebook (version 3 or earlier) Jupyter kernel # Go # gopherdata/gophernotes # $ go get -u github.
